    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <p>
                ​I am an undergraduate student from Queensland University of Technology studying Information Technology, majoring in Computer Science, currently in third year. I am working hard to achieve the best results and be a very valuable employee for the further development of Technology. 
                I am hoping to obtain employment in network security where I can pursue my passion for technology, use my skills and academic knowledge as an Information Technology student and perform the best in your company. 
                Throughout my whole life, I have been interested in learning and seeing new things. Even seeing technology improve and used in today's modern society. Technology has really impressed me and in which I have grown a passion in. Which is why I studied IT in high school and now in university.
